This is special broken version of tcplim to test valgrind

Valgrind failure example:

1. socat tcp-l:9998,reuseaddr,fork file:/dev/zero
2. valgrind ./tcplim 127.0.0.1 9999 127.0.0.1 9998 10000000 10000000 1000000000 1000000000 50
3. nc 127.0.0.1 9999 | pv > /dev/null
  48kB 0:00:00 [ 475kB/s] [  <=>           

